{
  "texts": [
    "Select the single best move that makes the most progress toward the goal; use any heuristic you judge appropriate (optimality not required).",
    "If multiple moves are equally good, you may choose any of them but do not undo the previous move.",
    "The goal is to arrange the board as follows: [[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6], [7, 8, 0]].",
    "The puzzle is guaranteed solvable.",
    "Your response must be only the single integer representing your chosen move."
  ]
}